{"tid":1815023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【印度版721恐襲】印度多處有學生上街示威　抗議蒙面人闖入大學校園施襲","createTime":"2020-01-07T08:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T08:23:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce6abc8d15cc54d997c03efb937200d69a90583c","tid":1815023,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1501416_1_L_20200107111928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1501416_1_L_20200107111928.jpg&h=d16f2fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501416-20200107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501416-20200107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=91ce68a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501416-20200107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5a658132\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501416-20200107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n印度多個城市有學生上街示威，抗議星期日晚上有超過100名蒙面人手持棍棒和磚頭等武器，闖入新德里一間大學襲擊學生和教師，導致超過30人受傷。示威者又指責警方執法不力，並無迅速回應襲擊事件。警方表示，已經鎖定部分襲擊者的身份。<br />\n<br />\n反對黨和受傷的學生指責，襲擊事件是與總理莫迪所屬執政印度人民黨有聯繫的學生組織所為。不過，被批評的學生組織否認指控，反而指責是敵對的左翼組織發動襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n在遇襲的大學，有學生發起在全國示威，抗議莫迪的政府早前完成《公民身份法》修正案的立法，認為修正案歧視穆斯林。"},{"pid":"49d34715f18ab1d0865e3c57f1df358200033364","tid":1815023,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"connect叉佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}